  "detailed_description": "Start your space expedition with Swing by - a game that will test your skills and reflexes! Become a master of spaceship control as you race through endless space. Your task is simple but challenging: collect valuable gems and win prizes while skillfully maneuvering through space.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/eff8ea8aa2da6d24187af1880ef55ba8.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/eff8ea8aa2da6d24187af1880ef55ba8.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/eff8ea8aa2da6d24187af1880ef55ba8.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>🎮 HOW TO PLAY</strong><br>use gamepad, keyboard or mouse to rotate the ship around the planet and thrust forward to far reaches of unexplored space. <br><i>Click and hold anywhere on screen or click and hold key on keyboard or gamepad to spin around the planet. Release when you want to go foward!</i><br>Practice your reflexes as you spin around the planet and collect valuable rewards and prove you're the best.<br><br>🚀 <strong>2D and 3D Game view</strong><br>Choose your gaming style between 2D and 3D perspectives. Experience the game in the way that suits you best.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/90cc79f51e071f9bf847c62ee7a1ed0f.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/90cc79f51e071f9bf847c62ee7a1ed0f.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/90cc79f51e071f9bf847c62ee7a1ed0f.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/d17cf3aae7090fe57dc3afd6296174e5.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/d17cf3aae7090fe57dc3afd6296174e5.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/d17cf3aae7090fe57dc3afd6296174e5.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>💎 <strong>Gems and Ranks</strong><br>Collect gems to unlock new levels and spaceships. Each level brings new challenges and exciting rewards for you to discover.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/a6758036d329c3e2053bd5f06dcd8e2e.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>🚢 <strong>Various Spaceships</strong><br>Unlock different spaceships to customize your gaming experience. Each ship has its own special characteristics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/cb7c44e0672b2f1146ad5a3077af56ae.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/cb7c44e0672b2f1146ad5a3077af56ae.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/cb7c44e0672b2f1146ad5a3077af56ae.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🏆 <strong>Leaderboards</strong><br>Compare your score to fellow space travelers around the universe<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/3eb033303d3abe16148fe95a0452d02b.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/3eb033303d3abe16148fe95a0452d02b.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/3eb033303d3abe16148fe95a0452d02b.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>🌐<strong>Multiplayer</strong><br>Join friends or challenge players around the world in exciting multiplayer battles. Show your skills and win galactic leadership!<br><br>Multiplayer is supported, only in local split screen mode up to 4 players can play together.<br>Note: Online multiplayer mode will be implemented in a future update.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/9f6ba7f9bdbc2f9a08d74936e2a29904.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/9f6ba7f9bdbc2f9a08d74936e2a29904.webm?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/9f6ba7f9bdbc2f9a08d74936e2a29904.mp4?t=1729510418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/9f12685679bb1607111f4110afe5fd42.poster.avif?t=1729510418\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2698600/extras/9f12